title: Game of Thrones Remix
description:
Remix of the Epic TV Show, "Game of Thrones". Inspired by the magical tunes of the original soundtrack by Ramin Djawadi; remixed by DJ AT (Pakistan).

An epic show, a soundtrack that's even better, and a taste of trance for the old gods... and the new!
